lead_paragraph: The U.S. turned over Qais al-Khazali, one of the suspected leaders of a Shiite insurgent group believed to be behind the kidnapping of Peter Moore, to Iraqi authorities.

headline.main: U.S. Transferred Detainee Before Hostage Release
headline.print_headline: U.S. Turned Over a Suspected Insurgent Leader to Iraqis Before a Hostage’s Release

byline.contributor: Jack Healy contributed reporting from New York.
